# Input

```html
<HTML>
  <Body>
    <BUTTON>Should be lowercased</BUTTON>
    <INPUT type="text">
    <SELECT></SELECT>
    <TEXTAREA></TEXTAREA>
    <Component>Should preserve casing</Component>
  </Body>
</HTML>

```


# Formatted

```html
<html>
	<body>
		<button>Should be lowercased</button>
		<input type="text">
		<select></select>
		<textarea></textarea>
		<Component>Should preserve casing</Component>
	</body>
</html>

```
